<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-1.1)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
