                        <div><p class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Topic: Shopping</p><p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-700">How often do you go shopping?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you love shopping ?.
-> Yes, i am shopping lover/ a big fan of shopping.
Where do you shop at ?.
+) I often shop at the supermarket centre
Why supermarket but not small shops ?.
1) Supermarket has air condition. It is pretty cool in the summer, and warm in the winter. It is comfortable
2) Supermarket offers various products to choose from sizes, types, materials, prices, ... 
3) The products have price tags on it. So you do not have to bargain. 
+) sometimes i shop at the convinient store 
Is convinient store far from your house/ How far/ How long does it take ?.
Convinient store is not far from my house. I can walk to the store for about 5 minutes. 
When do you go shopping ?. 
1. I usually go shopping at the weekend when i want to buy casual products like soap, brush, towel, washing power, ...  
Why not in other day ?. because i am always busy during the weeks with my job. It starts at 7.0 am to 5 pm every day since Monday to Friday. 
Do you prefer to go alone or with friends or family ?.Why ?
-> I often go shopping alone but i would love to go with my family. 
+) I want to spend more time with them since i do not have much time during the week.
+)  We can have small talk and take a photo. This create memories last forever. 
Why do you love shopping ?.
1. Shopping is my hobby. I really feel relaxed and it helps me to fresh my mind after a busy day.
2. I have worked very hard. Spending money on favourite items bring about (đem lại) the sense of achievement. (sense of life purpose beside work).

  






 









